title: Great Things Take Time
itunes:title: Great Things Take Time
description:
Episode 394 - We live in an instant world. Everything is delivered today or 10 minutes or less, etc. But success will never be instant, it takes time. The greatest things in life take time. Listen to this episode to learn how to train yourself to be okay with delaying your gratification.
